  "metaTitle": "Schluter-KERDI vs. RedGard | Arizona Shower Waterproofing",
  "metaDescription": "Which is best for waterproofing your Arizona shower? Compare Schluter-KERDI sheet membranes and RedGard liquid membranes for durability and shifting framing.",
  "author": "Alex Rivers",
  "status": "published",
  "publishedAt": "2026-05-11T08:00:00Z",
