  "metaTitle": "2024-2025 Bathroom Design Trends for Chandler, Arizona Homes",
  "metaDescription": "Explore 2024-2025 bathroom design trends in Chandler, AZ. Spa features, sustainable materials, minimalist design, wellness technology, and luxury fixtures trending now.",
  "author": "Alex Rivers",
